Titolo: Puyo Puyo Chronicle

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Puyo Puyo Chronicle (ぷよぷよクロニクル) is a puzzle video game developed by Sonic Team and published by Sega for the Nintendo 3DS, to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Puyo Puyo series. It is the first release featuring 3D models for characters instead of the traditional 2D.In addition of the traditional mechanics, it introduces role-playing elements, allowing to have up to three allies in team, as well as over 60 side missions and introduces a new protagonist, Ally.

Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: N/A
